title: Chalie Boy - I Look Good (edited).mp3
description:
Chalie Boy - I look good

Couldn't find it on here, so I figured I help out some.

It's edited, although there really aren't a lot of swear words in it anyway, so it's not a big deal.  I had to rip it from a music video, and I couldn't find one, even vevo, which was explicit, so save me the complaining please.

I'm not going to list a bitrate, because I'm not really sure what it was when I ripped it from the video, but it is definitely good, especially considering the source.
